OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781581669
OL,3,CCaptain of Russian shadow fleet tanker
OL,4,Cintercepted in Channel to appear in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe captain of a Russian shadow fleet
OL,8,Fvessel which was intercepted by
OL,9,FBritish troops in the English Channel
OL,10,Fwill appear in court charged with
OL,11,Fbreaching sanctions.
OL,13,FIndian national Ajay Pant, 38, has
OL,14,Fbeen charged with directly or
OL,15,Findirectly supplying or delivering by
OL,16,Fship prohibited oil or oil products
OL,17,Ffrom Russia to a third country in June
OL,18,F2026, in contravention of Regulation
OL,19,F46Z9B of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU
OL,20,FExit) Regulations 2019.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
