FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781581669
OL,3,CCaptain of Russian shadow fleet tanker
OL,4,Cintercepted in Channel to appear in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FHe will appear at Southampton
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday.
OL,10,FRoyal Marine commandos and officers
OL,11,Ffrom the National Crime Agency (NCA)
OL,12,Fseized the tanker Smyrtos in the
OL,13,FChannel early on Sunday in the first
OL,14,FUK-led operation to capture a
OL,15,Fsanctioned vessel and it has since
OL,16,Fbeen formally prevented from leaving
OL,17,Fthe UK.
OL,19,FThe 24 crew members, from Georgia and
OL,20,FIndia, remain on board the ship, which
OL,21,Fis anchored off Weymouth in Dorset.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
