FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781581669
OL,3,CCaptain of Russian shadow fleet tanker
OL,4,Cintercepted in Channel to appear in
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FJoanne Jakymec, chief Crown prosecutor
OL,8,Ffor the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,9,F(CPS), said: "The CPS has decided to
OL,10,Fprosecute Ajay Pant for breaching
OL,11,FRussian sanctions following a National
OL,12,FCrime Agency investigation and the
OL,13,Fseizure of the shadow oil tanker, MV
OL,14,FSmyrtos, travelling through the
OL,15,FEnglish Channel over the last weekend.
OL,17,F"We remind all concerned that criminal
OL,18,Fproceedings against Pant are active
OL,19,Fand he has the right to a fair trial.
